        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\nThanks Temoc.   I think it can be kept simpler just with this code below, when guard is disabled.\n\neventmanager/src/main/java/org/onap/policy/controlloop/eventmanager/ControlLoopOperationManager.java\n\nprivate void  storeOperationInDataBase(){\nboolean guardEnabled = \"false\".equalsIgnoreCase(PolicyEngine.manager.getEnvironmentProperty(\"guard.disabled\"));\n\nif (!guardEnabled){\n   return;\n}",
